cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.RO 

The paper deals with the classification of remote sensing images using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning models such as SegNet also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The exploitation of structural tensors for geometrical information could also relate to graphics (cs.GR) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories.
